        <scopecontent>
            <p>This collection documents the inventions and business activities of Joseph E. Burns, founder of the Burns Manufacturing Company in Syracuse, NY. It contains photographs, patents, product advertisements, and items which Burns either manufactured or used in the course of his work.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <userestrict>
            <p>The Erie Canal Museum is providing access to these materials for personal, educational, and research purposes only. Prior permission from the Erie Canal Museum is required for any other use.</p>
        </userestrict>
